"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president, in an interview, mentioned he wants to take Iran's oil but also said a deal could be made quickly. After a month of conflict in Iran, Trump's approach is not working well, according to a BBC editor.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President on Iran\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU., en una entrevista, dijo que quiere tomar el petr\u00f3leo de Ir\u00e1n pero tambi\u00e9n dijo que se puede hacer un trato r\u00e1pido. Despu\u00e9s de un mes de conflicto en Ir\u00e1n, la forma de Trump no est\u00e1 funcionando bien, seg\u00fan un editor de la BBC.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. sobre Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Italian Competition Authority accused luxury goods company LVMH of using sneaky marketing strategies.\",            \"english_title\": \"LVMH Accused of Sneaky Marketing\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Autoridad de Competencia de Italia acus\u00f3 a la empresa de productos de lujo LVMH de usar estrategias de marketing enga\u00f1osas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"LVMH acusada de marketing enga\u00f1oso\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Israeli Prime Minister said Cardinal Pierbattista Pizzaballa was asked not to enter a church for his safety.\",            \"english_title\": \"Cardinal Advised for Safety\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Primer Ministro de Israel dijo que al Cardenal Pierbattista Pizzaballa le pidieron no entrar a una iglesia por su seguridad.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cardenal aconsejado por seguridad\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Several people were reportedly hurt after attacks on aluminum sites in the UAE and Bahrain. The Israeli military confirmed it killed Ali Shoeib from a TV station linked to Hezbollah.\",            \"english_title\": \"Attacks in UAE and Bahrain\",            \"translated_version\": \"Varias personas resultaron heridas despu\u00e9s de ataques en sitios de aluminio en los EAU y Bahr\u00e9in. El ej\u00e9rcito israel\u00ed confirm\u00f3 que mat\u00f3 a Ali Shoeib de una estaci\u00f3n de TV vinculada a Hezbollah.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques en EAU y Bahr\u00e9in\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"France's anti-terrorism office took over an investigation immediately after paintings were stolen from a museum in Parma by four masked men at night.\",            \"english_title\": \"Art Theft in Parma\",            \"translated_version\": \"La oficina antiterrorista de Francia tom\u00f3 una investigaci\u00f3n inmediatamente despu\u00e9s de que pinturas fueron robadas de un museo en Parma por cuatro hombres enmascarados por la noche.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Robo de arte en Parma\"        }    ]}"